Control statements is used to Control the flow of the program

Types:
1)Selection statements
 1.if
 2.if else
 3.if else if
 4.nested if
 5.switch

 2)Looping statements
  1.for Loop
  2.while loop
  3.do while loop
  4.for each loop
  
 3)Jumping statements
  1.break ->switch,loop
  2.continue ->loop